2. Replace the import statement `import javax.enterprise.inject.spi.InjectionPoint;` with `import jakarta.enterprise.inject.spi.InjectionPoint;`

No changes are required in the `pom.xml` file for this specific update, as we are only updating the import statements. However, when migrating to Jakarta EE 9 and later versions, you would typically need to update the dependencies in the `pom.xml` file to use the Jakarta EE 9 and later versions of the APIs.

